*** 311,17 ***
   *
   * Since: 2.4

  gint
  g_vasprintf (gchar      **string,
!          gchar const *format,
!          va_list      args)
  {
    gint len;
    g_return_val_if_fail (string != NULL, -1);
  
! #if !defined(HAVE_GOOD_PRINTF)
  
    len = _g_gnulib_vasprintf (string, format, args);
    if (len < 0)
      *string = NULL;
